            <title>[CASSANDRA-11553] hadoop.cql3.CqlRecordWriter does not close cluster on reconnect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11553</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-10058&quot; title=&quot;Close Java driver Client object in Hadoop and Pig classes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-10058&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-10058&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; add session and cluster close to all places in hadoop except one place on reconnection.&lt;br/&gt;
