                            <comment id="15237143" author="iamaleksey" created="Tue, 12 Apr 2016 13:21:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix ver? Also, please go through the motions listed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1d_AzYQo74de9utbbpyXxW2w-b0__sFhC7b24ibiJqjw/edit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;, thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15237355" author="artem.aliev" created="Tue, 12 Apr 2016 15:14:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;CHANGES.txt: Always close cluster with connection in CqlRecordWriter (&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11553&quot; title=&quot;hadoop.cql3.CqlRecordWriter does not close cluster on reconnect&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-11553&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-11553&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15237398" author="alexliu68" created="Tue, 12 Apr 2016 15:37:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1, cluster close automatically close all session, so the session close is redundant.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
